thread.title: C. Sergom
thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da C. Sergom

author: C. Sergom
title: C. Sergom
text:
Overall amazing experience! Authentic designer eyeglass-wear at a fraction of the USA price. Superfast order fulfillment, packed with utmost care.
I ordered an Oliver Peoples FINLEY ESQ. OV 5298U 108 eyeglass frame on March 16, 2017, which was shipped on the 22nd and received in NJ, USA on March 23rd. The frame came with a beautiful OP case and cleaning cloth. Identical frame is sold in the US for more than twice what I paid for. THANK YOU, Otticanet.
